Color of axis label is set to be [axisLine.lineStyle.color](~.axisLine.lineStyle.color) by default. Callback function is supported, in the following format:

```js
(val: string) => Color
```

Parameter is the text of label, and return value is the color. See the following example:

```js
textStyle: {
color: function (value, index) {
return value >= 0 ? 'green' : 'red';
}
}
```

The color of the splitLine, which could be set separately.

